Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.69,Danna ga Nani Main,Hajime,0,0,0,,Você gostou dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.85,Danna ga Nani Main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sim.
